== 迴響 ==

[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]將謎擬Q評為Game Freak設計出來最卓越和令人心碎的寶可夢，並指出它在網路上具有大批愛好者<ref>{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/the-internet-has-fallen-in-love-with-pokemon-sun-and-mo-1783559863|title=The Internet Has Fallen In Love With Pokémon Sun and Moon's Pikachu Imposter|publisher=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|author=Patricia Hernandez|date=2016-07-13|access-date=2016-12-03|archive-date=2016-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161121194153/http://kotaku.com/the-internet-has-fallen-in-love-with-pokemon-sun-and-mo-1783559863|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國線上雜誌{{link-en|Inverse (網站)|Inverse (website)|Inverse}}的 Catrina Dennis也注意到這一點，並評論：「謎擬Q扣動了精靈寶可夢系列的玩家的心弦，它產生一股新的、令人著迷的力量」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.inverse.com/article/18330-pokemon-mimikyu-is-stealing-hearts|title=Pokemon Fans Are Going Nuts For Sad, Adorable Mimikyu|author=Catrina Dennis|publisher=''[[Inverse_(website)|Inverse]]''|date=2016-07-15|access-date=2016-12-10|archive-date=2016-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220073642/https://www.inverse.com/article/18330-pokemon-mimikyu-is-stealing-hearts|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{link-en|Paste (雜誌)|Paste (magazine)|Paste}}的Janine Hawkins認為引起網友關注的原因是角色設計的結果，「由於它楚楚可憐的脆弱特性，愛好者很直接地就接受了它……謎擬Q試著觸動我們的情感，而且很顯然地成功了。」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.pastemagazine.com/articles/2016/07/the-power-of-helplessness-why-everybody-loves-mimi.html|title=The Power of Helplessness: Why Everybody Loves Mimikyu and Hates Popplio|author=Janine Hawkins|publisher=''[[Paste_(magazine)|Paste]]''|date=2016-07-25|access-date=2016-12-10|archive-date=2016-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220123518/https://www.pastemagazine.com/articles/2016/07/the-power-of-helplessness-why-everybody-loves-mimi.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[Destructoid|Destructoid]]將謎擬Q列為其旗下員工最喜歡的阿羅拉地區寶可夢之一，表示「在很多人眼中，它可能是第七世代裡的耀眼明星」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.destructoid.com/here-are-destructoid-s-favorite-alolan-pokemon-403210.phtml|title=Here are Destructoid's favorite Alolan Pokemon|publisher=''[[Destructoid|Destructoid]]''|date=2016-12-06|access-date=2016-12-10|archive-date=2016-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220075936/https://www.destructoid.com/here-are-destructoid-s-favorite-alolan-pokemon-403210.phtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[Polygon|Polygon]]的Allegra Frank則撰文評論，謎擬Q可能是最獨特、最古怪的寶可夢之一<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.polygon.com/2016/7/19/12225262/pokemon-sun-and-moon-new-pokemon-mimikyu|title=Get to know Pokémon Sun and Moon's six newest Pokémon|publisher=''[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]]''|author=Allegra Frank|date=2016-07-19|access-date=2016-12-03|archive-date=2016-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161203101144/http://www.polygon.com/2016/7/19/12225262/pokemon-sun-and-moon-new-pokemon-mimikyu|dead-url=no}}</ref>。The Mary Sue的 Jessica Lachenal 則認為「謎擬Q的可愛之處正是它的神祕之處」。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.themarysue.com/pokemon-feels-trip-mimikyu-song/|title=Let’s Take a Pokémon Feels Trip With This Sad Mimikyu Song|author=Jessica Lachenal|location=[[The_Mary_Sue|The Mary Sue]]|date=2016-10-21|access-date=2016-12-03|archive-date=2016-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161207223940/http://www.themarysue.com/pokemon-feels-trip-mimikyu-song/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

一些愛好者推測，觀看謎擬Q的真面目後會產生負面影響的設定，可能是影射現實世界中導致多名觀眾引發急性光過敏症的[[3D龍事件|3D龍事件]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/the-theory-that-connects-a-banned-pokemon-episode-and-s-1789418475|title=The Theory That Connects A Banned Pokémon Episode And Scary Mimikyu|author=Brian Ashcraft|publisher=''[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]''|date=2016-11-28|access-date=2016-12-12|archive-date=2016-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161210144855/http://kotaku.com/the-theory-that-connects-a-banned-pokemon-episode-and-s-1789418475|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://br.ign.com/pokemon/43109/news/pokemon-teoria-bizarra-revela-quem-pode-ser-mimikyu|title=Pokémon: Teoria Bizzara Revela Quem Pode Ser Mimikyu|publisher=[[IGN|IGN Brasil]] (in Portuguese)|author=Thais Stagni|date=2016-12-11|access-date=2016-12-12|archive-date=2016-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161212130309/http://br.ign.com/pokemon/43109/news/pokemon-teoria-bizarra-revela-quem-pode-ser-mimikyu|dead-url=no}}</ref>

